Text: Charlotte's support came at the perfect time in my career journey. Her sharp, thoughtful feedback on my CV and LinkedIn gave me the clarity and confidence I needed to move forward. I know the work we did together will be a turning point in the near future. She’s not just a coach, she’s a genuine guide who listens, understands, and elevates. I’m truly grateful and highly recommend her to anyone looking to level up their CV, LinkedIn, or overall professional profile.
